/*Ce premier widget aura pour but d'afficher un album de PNL*/
import '../style/Widget1.css'

import React from 'react'

export default function Widget1() {
    return ( <
        div className = 'widget1_position' >
        <
        iframe src = "https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/0OrjrvwmdJ82zYJpJ46lUs?utm_source=generator"
        width = "100%"
        height = "380"
        frameBorder = "10"
        allowfullscreen = ""
        allow = "autoplay; 
        clipboard - write; encrypted - media; fullscreen; picture - in -picture " className='widget1_content'> <
        /iframe> <
        /div>
    )
}
